abstract_ssm: One certificate, dated 1880, stating that Julius Robinson has achieved the "Degree of Manhood" and is a beneficiary member of the Supreme Lodge of the Knights of Honor, a fraternal organization.  The certficate is given under the seal of the Knights of Honor Lodge No. 2115, New York City.
